<div id="main" class="container-fluid">
    <div class="home slide">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <h1>Amy Sandy Panyanouvong</h1>
            <h1>&amp;</h1>
            <h1>Kevin Richard May</h1>

            <h1 class="date">08.07.2016</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="event-info slide">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div>
                <h1>Event Info</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="google-map">
                <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/view?zoom=16&center=33.1412%2C-117.1404&key=AIzaSyAuHW1d-M01bWep8ARTLp2cRIa9UoqmxT8" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Green Gables Wedding Estate</h2>
                <p>134 Woodland Parkway, San Marcos, CA 92069</p>
                <p>Sunday the 7th of August, 2016 @ 4pm</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#moreInfoModal">Click for more info...</button>
            </div>
            <div id="moreInfoModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                            <h3 class="modal-title">EVENT INFORMATION</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <p>
                                The ceremony will begin at 4:00pm and will take place outside, weather
                                permitting. Dinner and dancing will follow shortly after. Bring your
                                party pants/dresses people, it’s going to be a good ole’ time. Dress is
                                semiformal; bow ties and/or bolo ties are encouraged.
                            </p>
                            <hr>
                            <p>
                                Green Gables Wedding Estate is located in San Marcos, about 30 minutes
                                north of downtown San Diego just off Highway 78.  Ample parking will
                                be available on site.
                                <br>
                                Beer and Wine will be served at the reception by a licensed bartender.
                                If you are over the age of 21 and wish to partake, please make sure to
                                bring your ID with you.
                            </p>
                            <hr>
                            <p>
                                If you are joining us from out of town, you may wish to book a hotel reservation.
                                Some hotels we can recommend that are located closer to the venue include:
                                <br>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="http://hamptoninn3.hilton.com/en/hotels/california/hampton-inn-san-marcos-SANSMHX/index.html" target="_blank">Hampton Inn San Marcos ($)</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/sanmc-residence-inn-san-diego-north-san-marcos/" target="_blank">Residence Inn by Marriott San Diego North San Marcos ($$)</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="http://www.lakehousehotelandresort.com/" target="_blank">Lakehouse Hotel and Resort ($$$)</a></li>
                                </ul>
                                Many other lodging accommodations are available closer to downtown San Diego;
                                we recommend you look for lodging there if you’re planning on exploring the
                                city a bunch over the weekend.
                            </p>
                            <hr>
                            <p>
                                Any questions, comments, concerns, playlist requests, or accommodation inquiries,
                                feel free to contact Amy &amp; Kevin:
                                <a href="mailto:kevinandamymay@gmail.com?Subject=Wedding%20Inquiry" target="_top">
                                    kevinandamymay@gmail.com
                                </a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="our-story slide">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <h1>Our Story</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <%= image_tag 'climbing' %>
                    <p>
                        Amy &amp; Kevin first met at a pool hall in 2012.
                        Over the next year Amy &amp; Kevin developed a friendship
                        that would become the basis of their relationship.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <%= image_tag 'family' %>
                    <p>
                        On November 17th, 2013 Amy &amp; Kevin got engaged. On July
                        5th, 2015 they welcomed the beautiful Emma who has made their
                        relationship even stronger.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

