    <div class="rsvp slide">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div>
                <h1>R.S.V.P</h1>

                <p>Please enter your email address to search for your invitation.</p>

                <p>If you unable to complete your invitation online, please contact us.</p>

                <form class="form-inline">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control email" name="email" placeholder="Email">
                    </div>
                    <button id="submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-default search" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#rsvp-modal">Search</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div id="rsvp-modal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <form id="invitation-form">
                            <div class="modal-header">
                                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                                <h3 class="modal-title">R.S.V.P</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-body">
                                <p id="invitation-name"></p>
                                <p id="invitation-content">
                                    Please join us in celebrating our wedding on Sunday the 7th of August, 2016 at 4pm.
                                </p>
                                <p id="invitation-select">Please select who will be attending and then click submit.</p>

                                <input id="invitation-id" type="hidden"></input>
                                <div id="invitees"></div>
                                <div id="plus-one" class="form-group plus-one">
                                    <input id="plus-one-going" class="plus-one-going" name="invitation[plus_one_going]" type="checkbox" value="true"></input>
                                    <input id="plus-one-name" name="invitation[plus_one_name]" class="plus-one-name form-control" type="text" placeholder="Guest name" disabled="true"></input>
                                    <span class="plus-one-name-required">Required</span>
                                </div>

                                <p id="already-responded">
                                    You have already responded.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    If you wish to change your response please contact us directly as soon as possible.
                                </p>

                                <p id="not-found">We were unable to find an invitation for <span id="not-found-email" /></p>
                                <p id="contact-us">Please contact us directly.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer">
                                <button id="invitation-submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Submit</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="rsvp-success-modal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                            <h3 class="modal-title">Thank You</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <p>Thank you for your response. We will e-mail you to confirm your response.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="rsvp-failure-modal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                            <h3 class="modal-title">Error</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <p>There was an error processing your response. Please contact us directly as soon as possible.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="registry slide">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <h1>Registry</h1>

            <p>
                As we have been living together for quite some time now we are requesting that rather than
                buying a gift, can you please help make our honeymoon unforgetable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Click below to visit our honeyfund site.
            </p>
            <p>
                Honeyfund gives you the option to use your credit/debit card. However, if you prefer to give
                cash/check then please choose that as your payment option on their site.
            </p>
            <p>
                Thank you in advance.
                <h2>Amy &amp; Kevin</h2>
            </p>

            <div style="width:200px;margin:0 auto;">
                <a href="http://www.honeyfund.com/wedding/MayWedding" style="text-align:left;background:url('http://www.honeyfund.com/share/honeyfund3.png') no-repeat;display:block;width:200px;height:100px;text-indent:-9999em;" target="_blank">Visit our honeyfund at Honeyfund.com, the free honeymoon registry</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
